{
  "stem": "26983.10",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Auschwitz, it was most important to keep, somehow--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--clean, and because this was the very first one who were beaten up or sent to the crematorium, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these Musulmans, you could see, oh, he-- he's on the way to the crematorium-- or, as we called it in our children language, with one leg in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we tried--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to look like it--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And not to be one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We tried, thanks to the education we got from Theresienstadt and mainly from Fredy Hirsch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very punctually on it that we should be always clean and correct.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, how-- what we have done all together in Auschwitz-- everyone tried to get out of heavy, physical work, which you couldn't endure.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were lucky that our work wasn't killing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even this work we had to do, everyone tried to work as less as possible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And be aware.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's say we took breaks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the minute we saw some SS, we said, achtzehn. 'Achtzehn' means 18, but it sounds like 'achtung,' beware.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we suddenly shouted, achtzehn, which sounds like achtung.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And achtung means beware.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then at once, of course, we pretended that we worked with all our might.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it depended who was your kapo or who was supervising your work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If he was good natured, so he, himself said, oh, pretend or show off that you work with the last-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that you do something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are working hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the danger was you are caught that you don't work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you have to be very clever to pretend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you can, not to work at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my philosophy--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Losing strength.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
